Show HN: Betterpipe – Easy logging for ML deployments
text: Betterpipe is a python package that pipes your log output (e.g. print statements) to an external file that is viewable to you (link emailed upon file creation). This means that regardless of how you choose to deploy your models (banana.dev/replicate/etc.), you can easily see the output.
